{"tid":2169160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"間接宣戰！官媒稱黃海軍事演習是為「可能與美國發生的軍事衝突作準備」","createTime":"2020-08-22T09:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T12:19:11.000Z","uid":48040,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"99a5cdc18e83d3fe0da8001cfdd35557cb23f793","tid":2169160,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"中國山東海事局以及海南海事局官網通報，解放軍將於今(22)日起至26日，以及本月24日至29日，分別於黃海青島至連雲港以東海域、海南島東南部海域進行實彈軍事演訓活動。<br />\n<br />\n根據《東方網》報導，此次解放軍於今日到26日在東海的演訓，是一個月內第二次的實彈射擊演習，另若以近一個月的動向來看，解放軍已公布至少9場包括演習在內的軍事訓練活動。山東海事局在公告中特別指出，「此次實彈打靶覆蓋範圍大、彈藥威力大，擅自出海被誤炸誤傷的危險極大。如有擅自出海造成危險者，後果自負」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aQD4NU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aQD4NU&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=f84ff63c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aQD4NU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">而昨日官媒表示，黃海演習是「為可能與美國發生的軍事衝突作準備」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1296840270730768384?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1296840270730768384%3Fs%3D20&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=1692624b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1296840270730768384%3Fs%3D20&h=e4b53eea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1296840270730768384?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>解放軍近日的軍演及訓練：</ins><br />\n<br />\n8/22-29<br />\n海南島東南部海域進行實彈軍事演訓<br />\n<br />\n8/22-26<br />\n山東青島至連雲港以東海域大型實彈射擊演習<br />\n<br />\n8/18<br />\n西藏軍區公佈近日舉行多兵種、多火器高原實彈射擊演練<br />\n<br />\n8/16-17<br />\n浙江舟山海區岱山水道北面海域實彈射擊訓練<br />\n<br />\n8/16<br />\n駐港部隊「惠州艦」近日在南海進行軍事訓練<br />\n<br />\n8/14-15<br />\n東部戰區在台海及南北兩端連續組織實戰化演習<br />\n<br />\n8/11-13<br />\n浙江舟山島實彈搶灘登陸演習<br />\n<br />\n7/25-8/2<br />\n雷州半島以西海域組織實彈打靶訓練<br />\n<br />\n7/30<br />\n國防部發言人證實，南部戰區近日組織轟炸機，在南海展晝夜間高強度訓練"},{"pid":"4bb7bedf8449f311c705784ef519bcda8705f035","tid":2169160,"uid":62749,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"現身至算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f931a99d5b6d98b1693c840f8c0d9378c14ca444","tid":2169160,"uid":63,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"打啦屌你老母 間接宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d250710da8eedf32153c42e75d3349670bc86fde","tid":2169160,"uid":160551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"差好遠wo 邊撚到夠擔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d065be033576f1180beb82ec72a8968cc7596a","tid":2169160,"uid":48040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f931a99d5b6d98b1693c840f8c0d9378c14ca444","tid":2169160,"uid":63,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:27:31.000Z","msg":"打啦屌你老母 間接宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"又要威又要戴頭盔"},{"pid":"01fbbc66db39b23a088a092b6e9d068073b39801","tid":2169160,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d250710da8eedf32153c42e75d3349670bc86fde","tid":2169160,"uid":160551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"差好遠wo 邊撚到夠擔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"人有多大膽，地有多大產"},{"pid":"2a7b6bfce0b6f8167eb1a38ea8fa3a5668d68546","tid":2169160,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"離海岸線幾遠都無講"},{"pid":"1cb291942181a055513bc0b2110ab481c94f9d66","tid":2169160,"uid":48040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"歡迎關注我們的知識型Youtube Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5sZA3tD-4-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F